src:
Her har Miljøpakken åpnet 72 gratis parkeringsplasser
07 Nov 2019, 12:18 by Martin Andersen
Pendlerparkeringa på Være ligger rett utenfor bommen.
Denne uken åpnet den nye pendlerparkeringa, rett utenfor bommen på Være.
text:
Here, the Environmental Package has opened 72 free parking spaces
07 Nov 2019, 12:18 by Martin Andersen
The commuter parking at Være is just outside the boom.
This week, the new commuter car park opened, just off the boom at Være.
